{
  "Modeling with Derivatives": "利用衍生工具建模",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "The cost function C(x) = 0.01x^2 + 5x + 1000. What is the marginal cost at x = 100?": "成本函数C(x) = 0.01x__2 + 5x+ 1000。x = 100的边际成本是多少?",
  "Marginal cost = C'(x) = 0.02x + 5. At x = 100: C'(100) = 2 + 5 = $7 per unit.": "边际成本 = C'(x) = 0.02x + 5. 在x = 100: C'(100) = 2 + 5 = 每单位7美元。",
  "Newton's law of cooling states dT/dt = -k(T - T_env). If T_env = 20 and k = 0.1, what is the cooling rate when T = 80?": "牛顿冷却法则dT/dt = -k(T- T_env). 如果T_env = 20和k = 0.1, 当T = 80时冷却率是多少?",
  "dT/dt = -0.1(80 - 20) = -0.1(60) = -6 degrees/min.": "dT/dt = -0.1(80-20) = -0.1(60) = -6度/分钟。",
  "A radioactive substance has dN/dt = -0.05N. If N(0) = 200, what is N(10)?": "放射性物质有dN/dt = - 0.05N。如果N(0) = 200,那N(10)是什么?",
  "Solution: N(t) = 200e^(-0.05t). At t = 10: N(10) = 200e^(-0.5) (approximately 121.3).": "溶液: N(t) = 200e(- 0.05t). t = 10: N(10) = 200e(-0.5). (约121.3)。",
  "A marketing model shows that sales S(a) = 1000 - 800e^(-0.01a), where a is advertising dollars spent. What is the marginal return on advertising at a = $200?": "一种营销模式表明,销售S(a)=1000-800e(-0.01a),其中广告花费的是美元。广告的边际回报是多少?",
  "S'(a) = 800 * 0.01 * e^(-0.01a) = 8e^(-0.01a). At a = 200: S'(200) = 8e^(-2) sales per additional dollar (approximately 1.08 sales/dollar).": "S'(a) = 800 * 0.01 * e(-0.01a) = 8 e(- 0.01a) = 8 e(- 0.01a). 在 a = 200: S'(200) = 8 e(-2) 每增加一美元(约1.08 销售额/美元)的销售额。",
  "A company's growth follows logistic growth: P(t) = 500/(1 + 9e^(-0.5t)). What is the growth rate at t = 0?": "公司的增长随着物流的增长而变化:P(t)=500/(1+9e(-0.5t))。 t=0的增长率是多少?",
  "P'(t) = 500 * 9 * 0.5 * e^(-0.5t)/(1+9e^(-0.5t))^2 = 2250e^(-0.5t)/(1+9e^(-0.5t))^2. At t = 0: P'(0) = 2250(1)/(10)^2 = 2250/100 = 22.5.": "P'(t) = 500 * 9 * 0.5 * e(- 0.5t) /(1+9e(- 0.5t)) 2 = 2250e(- 0.5t) /(1+9e(- 0.5t)) 。 t = 0: P'(0) = 2250(1)/(10) /2 = 2250/100 = 22.5。",
  "An investment depreciates: V(t) = 50000 * (0.85)^t dollars. What is the rate of depreciation at t = 3 years?": "投资折旧率: V(t) = 50 000 * (0.85美元) 。t = 3 年的折旧率是多少?",
  "V'(t) = 50000 * (0.85)^t * ln(0.85). At t = 3: V'(3) = 50000 * ln(0.85) * (0.85)^3. Since ln(0.85) < 0, this is negative (approximately -$4,990/year).": "V'(t) = 50000 * (0.85) * * in(0.85).t = 3: V'(3) = 50000 * In(0.85) * (0.85)3。由于在(0.85) < 0,这是负数(约为 - 4 990美元/年)。",
  "A chemical reaction rate is given by r = k[A]^2[B], where k = 0.5. If [A] = 2 mol/L decreasing at 0.1 mol/L/s and [B] = 3 mol/L increasing at 0.05 mol/L/s, what is dr/dt?": "化学反应率由 r = k[A]%2[B] 给出, k = 0.5。如果 [A] = 2 毫升/升,减少0.1毫升/升, [B] = 3 毫升/升,增加0.05毫升/升,那么什么是Dr/dt?",
  "r = 0.5A^2*B. dr/dt = 0.5[2A*B*dA/dt + A^2*dB/dt] = 0.5[2(2)(3)(-0.1) + (4)(0.05)] = 0.5[-1.2 + 0.2] = 0.5(-1) = -0.5.": "r = 0.5A2*B. Dr/dt = 0.5[2A*B*dA/dt + A2*dB/dt] = 0.5[2(2)(3)-0.1) + (4)(0.05)] = 0.5[1.2+0.2] = 0.5(-1) = -0.5。"
